Resampling and performance metrics

caret will manage the training, tuning, and assessment of the models. Resampling and performance metrics caret will manage the training, tuning, and assessment of the models. We must specify a resampling scheme and a primary performance metric. Let’s use 5-fold cross-validation with 3-repeats. Our primary performance metric will be RMSE.

my_ctrl <- trainControl(method = "repeatedcv", number = 5, repeats = 3,savePredictions = TRUE)

my_metric <- "RMSE"

##1.Linear methods ##1a)All categorical and continuous inputs - linear additive features

set.seed(2021)

fit_lm_1a <- train(logresponse~.-rowid-response-outcome,
                  data =log_all,
                  method = "lm",
                  metric = my_metric,
                  preProcess = c("center", "scale"),
                  trControl = my_ctrl)
